snippet: A shipment of much-needed groceries, experiments and other items rocketed toward the International Space Station for the first time in months.
abstract: Rocket containing much-needed supplies for International Space Station launches successfully; after several failed attempts, delivery will be first shipment to reach astronauts since April 2015.
lead_paragraph: A shipment of much-needed groceries, experiments and other items rocketed toward the International Space Station for the first time in months.

headline.main: Supplies Bound for Space Station After Successful Launch
headline.print_headline: For the First Time in Months, a Space Station Supply Rocket Makes a Successful Launch
